result.name: Thai Farmer Restaurant

reviews.text: Had mango sticky rice, was pretty savoury. Nice atmosphere and okay service, depends who you get, can be nice or can be hostile. Green curry is nice, red curry is okay. All round average.
A small restaurant with app 16 seats capacity. Good and typical Thai food, reasonable price and good service
When I always visit in Hongkong I dont Hesitate to visit here in Thai restaurant the best and authentic Thai food here and you really loved it.
Good (but spicy!) food - there is a wide selection of classic Thai dishes as well as drinks. The staff was very helpful and prompt as well. Worth a visit!
Nice place to taste Thai food.
